    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://phoenix.craigslist.org/wvl/ret/6046773954.html"></div>
        </div>
Fuego is seeking a Store Manager for our store in the Scottsdale Fashion Square Mall.<br>
<br>
Boutique retail management experience is preferred but not required. We're a fairly young retailer, but we're growing, and we need talent to help us. We don't necessarily need someone who can fill up a resume five pages deep, but we need someone who understands retail, knows how to manage a small group of quirky people, and wants to earn advancement by being great.<br>
<br>
If you're an Assistant Store Manager ready to move up, or an experienced manager ready for a change, find out more about what we offer by visiting www.shopfuego.com.<br>
<br>
Apply online now by clicking this link:<br>
<a href="https://calendarclub.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/c9d68b2b-658e-75ce-bd9e-f0623bcb9b39/apply?source=474113-CS-5016" rel="nofollow">https://calendarclub.clearcompany.com/careers/jobs/c9d68b2b-658e-75ce-bd9e-f0623bcb9b39/apply?source=474113-CS-5016</a><br>
<br>
$35-40k/yr + benefits + bonus potential.    </section>

